title: American Tower Plans Third Quarter 2015 Earnings Release and Conference Call
text:
American Tower Plans Third Quarter 2015 Earnings Release and Conference Call October 05, 2015 04:30 PM Eastern Daylight Time 
BOSTON--( BUSINESS WIRE )--American Tower Corporation (NYSE: AMT) announced today that the press announcement of its third quarter 2015 results is scheduled to be released to the news services at 7:00 a.m. ET on Thursday, October 29, 2015. In addition, the Company has scheduled a conference call at 8:30 a.m. ET on Thursday, October 29, 2015 to discuss its results.
